OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLonger school days trialled
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin Wales education overhaul
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A longer school day will be trialled as
OL,6, part of plans to overhaul education to 
OL,7, fit in with work patterns and family   
OL,8, life.                                  
OL,10,FFourteen schools will take part in a   
OL,11,Fpilot scheme, adding an extra five     
OL,12,Fhours a week for groups of pupils.     
OL,14,FThe Welsh government also said it      
OL,15,Fwanted a discussion on school terms,   
OL,16,Fincluding a shorter summer holiday.    
OL,18,FOne teaching union called it a "pet    
OL,19,Fproject" and warned schools were at    
OL,20,F"breaking point".                      
